{{Top|leg}}
The '''AR-1''' was a specially designed [[Rifle/Legends|rifle]] manufactured by [[Greff-Timms Industrial/Legends|Greff-Timms Industrial]] for the [[Antarian Rangers/Legends|Antarian Rangers]]. A powerful, long-range rifle, it featured a signal flare launch setting and a [[Barrel/Legends|barrel]] mount that could be fitted with either a [[Glowrod/Legends|glowrod]] or a [[Vibrobayonet/Legends|vibro-bayonet]].

